Tic-Tac-Toe Two Player Support

Tic-Tac-Toe Two Player is a tic tac toe game for Apple Watch with fun themes.

Frequently Asked Questions

How do I change the theme?
Open the app and tap the theme button to swap the classic X and O for animal icons and other styles.

How do I start a new game?
Finish the current round or tap New Game from the game screen.

Which devices are supported?
Tic-Tac-Toe Two Player runs on Apple Watch. Check the App Store listing for the minimum watchOS version.

Does the app collect my data?
No. The app collects nothing. See the privacy policy for details.

